  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 战争是如何引起的",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_3135-3190",
          "range": "3135-3190",
          "rangeStart": 3135,
          "rangeEnd": 3190,
          "markText": "假如你容许任何人在锅炉下面不断地加煤，直到蒸汽压力已经超过了危险点，则引起任何爆炸的真正责任也就应该由你负担。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1718158809,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-12 10:20:09",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3135&rangeEnd=3190",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3135&rangeEnd=3190"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_3135-3190",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "3135-3190",
      "markText": "假如你容许任何人在锅炉下面不断地加煤，直到蒸汽压力已经超过了危险点，则引起任何爆炸的真正责任也就应该由你负担。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3135&rangeEnd=3190",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3135&rangeEnd=3190"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_11_6424-6457",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6424-6457",
      "markText": "两国高级将领的自我陶醉也都已达到了致命的程度，这是他们失败的主因。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6424&rangeEnd=6457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6424&rangeEnd=6457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_11_7349-7440",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7349-7440",
      "markText": "总而言之，德国陆军之所以能获得如此惊人的胜利，并非因为他们拥有压倒性的数量优势，也非因为他们在组织形态上已经彻底现代化，而是因为他们要比对方略高一筹，这个程度虽然不大，但却非常重要。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7349&rangeEnd=7440",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7349&rangeEnd=7440"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_11_4391-4440",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "4391-4440",
      "markText": "因为大多数人在思想上也还是摆脱不了1918年的旧观念，并且也像英国人一样，把法国陆军估计得太高了。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4391&rangeEnd=4440",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4391&rangeEnd=4440"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_11_10271-10293",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "10271-10293",
      "markText": "总之，轴心方面的命运就要看战争能否速决而定。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=10271&rangeEnd=10293",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=10271&rangeEnd=10293"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_1718-1757",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1718-1757",
      "markText": "这些文件显示出德国人对于他们自己有无能力进行一次全面战争是深感怀疑和不信任的。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1718&rangeEnd=1757",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1718&rangeEnd=1757"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_5694-5790",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5694-5790",
      "markText": "最初他并不想对波兰采取行动——尽管该国所据有的德国失地是面积最大的。波兰，也像匈牙利一样，曾经帮助希特勒威胁捷克的后方，所以也就促使捷克不得不向希特勒屈服——而且波兰也乘机获得了一片捷克的领土",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5694&rangeEnd=5790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5694&rangeEnd=5790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_8758-8783",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "8758-8783",
      "markText": "这种冲动是太典型化了，民族的命运常常是这样决定的。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8758&rangeEnd=8783",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8758&rangeEnd=8783"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_10833-10904",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "10833-10904",
      "markText": "反之，它却激起了英国人的“牛脾气”——那是一种盲目的决心，不计一切后果。在这种感情激动的情况之下，张伯伦也就不可能坐视，否则不仅失言而且丢脸。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10833&rangeEnd=10904",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10833&rangeEnd=10904"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_11_5657-5696",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "5657-5696",
      "markText": "波兰的领袖们也仍然深信大量骑兵的价值，并对骑兵冲锋的可能性寄以一种病态的信仰。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5657&rangeEnd=5696",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5657&rangeEnd=5696"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_6_1337-1370",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1337-1370",
      "markText": "“欧洲文明列车虽已从黑暗的隧道中冲出，眼前的光明却只是一片幻影。”",
      "totalCount": 121,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1337&rangeEnd=1370",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1337&rangeEnd=1370"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_19_2982-3023",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2982-3023",
      "markText": "因为戈林曾向希特勒保证他的空军能够阻止英国海军的干扰，并同时把英国空军逐出天空以外",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2982&rangeEnd=3023",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2982&rangeEnd=3023"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_11_1413-1471",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1413-1471",
      "markText": "关于法国的陆军却存在着更大的幻想。丘吉尔本人，在1938年4月14日曾经形容它是“欧洲训练最完善和机动最可靠的兵力”",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1413&rangeEnd=1471",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1413&rangeEnd=1471"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_3262-3355",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "3262-3355",
      "markText": "自从1933年希特勒当权之后，英法两国政府对于这个危险的独裁者所作的让步远超过他们过去对于德国前民主政府。每次他们都表现出由于怕麻烦而把困难问题搁置起来——为了眼前的舒适而不惜牺牲将来。",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3262&rangeEnd=3355",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=3262&rangeEnd=3355"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_9205-9230",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "9205-9230",
      "markText": "因为这些国家害怕苏联军队的增援即无异于外敌的侵入。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9205&rangeEnd=9230",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9205&rangeEnd=9230"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_20_9027-9126",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "9027-9126",
      "markText": "4月6日，德军侵入希腊，于是英国人又迅速地被迫作第二次的“敦刻尔克”。他们几乎全军覆没，经过了极大的困难，才从海上勉强撤退出来，但是德军仍然俘获了12000人与他们所有的坦克，以及其他装备的大部分。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9027&rangeEnd=9126",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9027&rangeEnd=9126"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_8919-8991",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "8919-8991",
      "markText": "张伯伦对于苏联具有强烈的厌恶心理，而哈里法克斯则具有强烈的宗教性反感，而他们两人对于苏联的实力估计过低，其程度恰与对于波兰的实力估计过高如出一辙",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8919&rangeEnd=8991",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8919&rangeEnd=8991"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_10_2652-2674",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2652-2674",
      "markText": "成功毒素的累积作用已经使他丧失了戒惧的心理。",
      "totalCount": 100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2652&rangeEnd=2674",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2652&rangeEnd=2674"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_11_5785-5847",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "5785-5847",
      "markText": "在第一次世界大战时，所有各国的陆军仍然继续维持着大量的骑兵，并希望有一显身手的机会，那可以算是那次静态战争中的一个极大讽刺。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5785&rangeEnd=5847",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5785&rangeEnd=5847"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35991907_18_10495-10580",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "10495-10580",
      "markText": "古德里安不仅学会了独立使用装甲部队行战略突穿的理论，而且对于此种理论的实践具有狂热的信心，以后又能不顾上级一切的制止而坚决奋斗到底，这样才把法军统帅部的一切计算都推翻了。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35991907&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=10495&rangeEnd=10580",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/98832770722531639889d34?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=10495&rangeEnd=10580"
    }
  ],
